  %h1 Speakers

  %p.nutshell Covering the latest technologies, Jon Buda will be speaking about mobile performance while Shay Howe will be speaking about modular HTML and CSS.  
  
  %section.speaker
  
    %h2 Jon Buda
    %h4 Speed by Design &ndash; Keep the Mobile Web Quick

    %p As attention spans are heading towards zero and more and more of the population is constantly on-the-go, optimizing your mobile websites to load quickly and efficiently can make an enormous difference in visitor engagement, and most importantly, your bottom-line. Designing for performance should be a top-priority in keeping your visitors happy and allowing them do what they need to do quickly.

    %p You&#8217;ll learn a few techniques on how to keep your mobile websites lean and loading quickly, how page speed is actually a component of good UX, how to test and benchmark under various network conditions, and how slow loading times can turn away visitors and potential paying customers.

    %aside.group
      
