      %img.speaker-img(src="assets/img/jon-buda.jpg" alt="Jon Buda")

      %p <a href="http://jonbuda.com/">Jon Buda</a> is web developer who loves to design, or a designer who loves to code &ndash; depending on the day. He enjoys solving problems holistically, thinking about back-end, front-end, and design all as equally important parts in crafting great experiences. He helps to organize <a href="http://refreshchi.org/" rel="nofollow">Refresh Chicago</a> and is currently working with <a href="http://www.tablexi.com/" rel="nofollow">Table XI</a>.

      %p
